orangepi-ubuntu-builder (2.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of Orange Pi 5 Plus Ubuntu Builder
  * Features include:
    - Custom kernel building with hardware optimization
    - U-Boot bootloader compilation and installation
    - Ubuntu rootfs creation with debootstrap
    - Mali G610 GPU driver support (Panfrost/Mesa)
    - Vulkan and OpenCL support
    - Bootable image generation
    - Interactive menu system
    - Comprehensive dependency management
  * Supports Orange Pi 5 Plus with RK3588 SoC
  * Includes patches for Mali GPU acceleration
  * Automated build process with error handling

 -- Orange Pi Builder <builder@orangepi.org>  Mon, 08 Jul 2025 12:00:00 +0000
